{
  "stem": "12447.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "How we managed, I don't really remember very well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But we lived in this one-room apartment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We had a, a nice-sized terrace that faced the street.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I spent a lot of hours playing outside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I remember that part.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I remember my father going to work in the morning and coming back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I remember he used to take me to shul.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[CRYING] [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SOBBING] I remember, [CRYING] [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] remember my sister.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We used to play.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The first real memory what I have of-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was my birthday.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I don't remember which birthday it was, but they made me a nice party.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They even bought me a little ring with my initials on it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I remember we used to, with my sister, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] sometimes steal the goodies when my parents went away.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We-- they used to, like-- we didn't have much of sweets, chocolate or sugar and all that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But I remember when they went, we used to dig in into the hidden places and take out some sugar and lick it up.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And that was before I was able to go to school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Now, I remember the death of this Polish marshal that ruled Poland-- Marshal Pilsudski.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I remember his funeral very well, which was in 1935.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I believe it was in November.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I went with my father to see this funeral-- which whole Poland was all in mourning because of this marshal.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I distinctly remember that point.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It just stuck in my memory, that particular thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now other things-- getting farther, I remember my family, my uncles, my grandparents on my mother's side.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
